00:18:27.933 --> 00:18:33.599 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:65%
So, first it means that we
now have more than seventy

00:18:33.666 --> 00:18:38.200 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:73%
different aspects about WCAG
that at least three different

00:18:38.266 --> 00:18:40.766 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:68%
