00:19:41.566 --> 00:19:45.633 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:63%
So, the other two vendors
have now products that

00:19:45.700 --> 00:19:49.833 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:60%
include conformance
testing using ACT Rules,

00:19:49.900 --> 00:19:54.333 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:58%
manual testing
methodologies that also

00:19:54.400 --> 00:19:57.166 align:middle line:85% position:50% size:45%
